                            <td>4,370,005.6 km</td>
                        </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Mass:</td>
                            <td>1.99 × 10^30 kg (333,060 Earths)</td>
                        </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Surface Temperature:</td>
                            <td>5,500 °C</td>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
            </table>
        </p>

